<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Irishman" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Irishman,</orth> a native of Ireland: <cit><quote>trust an I. with my aqua-vitae bottle,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.318" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 318</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.2.71" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 2, 71</bibl>. Pl. <emph>Irishmen</emph> == Irish: <cit><quote>try your hap against the Irishmen,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.314" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 314</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>